parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EPS can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn or lock up, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The power steering warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn or locks up
the vehicle is hard to maneuver
the steering wheel shakes or vibrates
and the EPS system fails intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering assist motor can cause the EPS system to fail, leading to a loss of power steering assist, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The power steering warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the EPS system fails
and the power steering assist motor needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the EPS system to fail, leading to a loss of power steering assist, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The power steering warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the EPS system fails
and the steering column needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlight electrical system can cause the headlights to malfunction, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Headlights fail to turn on
headlights turn on and off intermittently
smoke comes from under the hood when headlights are used.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the brake lights can cause confusion for other drivers, leading to increased risk of rear-end collisions.
symptoms: Brake lights stay on even when the brake pedal is not pressed
brake lights do not turn on when the brake pedal is pressed
brake lights flash on and off intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal sensor can cause the brake lights to malfunction, leading to increased risk of rear-end collisions.
symptoms: Brake lights stay on even when the brake pedal is not pressed
brake lights do not turn on when the brake pedal is pressed
brake lights flash on and off intermittently.
